data.description: This home has been completely remodeled and is like having a brand-new lakefront home. The new kitchen has granite counters, new cabinets, new stainless-steel appliances, and tile backsplash. The bathrooms have new vanities, toilets, light fixtures, and tile work in the showers. There is also luxury vinyl tile throughout and crown molding. The roof, ac, water heater, electric panel, and windows are also new. Did I mention that it's on a lake (no flood zone) with a 1/3 of an acre lot? This home is one of a kind so don't wait! make an appointment to see it for yourself.  Home has a remediated sinkhole with engineer's report and is fully insurable.
